2 G.S. 130A-336.1 or the Authorized On-Site Wastewater Evaluator permit option pursuant to
3 G.S. 130A-336.2. This requirement shall not apply to a manufactured residence exhibited for sale
4 or stored for later sale and intended to be located at another site after sale.
5 (b) The local health department shall issue a construction authorization authorizing work
6 to proceed and the installation or repair of a wastewater system when it has determined after a
